metadata.name: Psst...Dont forget to say GM
metadata.description:
GM GM 🫡  
வணக்கம் 🙏🏼

01 DEC 2022

I visualized this based on a shape I saw in an interesting QQL (by Tyler Hobbs) I generated few months ago.

Was just a fun meme sketch I used to say GM & had no idea of minting it.

But then I thought it would be nice if more people can own this.

now sharing it with you all for free, as saying GM and GM memes/arts are one of the things that are keeping our hopes up in these tough times. 

FOR THE CULTURE!  
FOR THE LOVE OF PEPE!

Thank You 🙏🏼  
VALIPOKKANN 🫶🏾🫂

நன்றி 🙏🏼  
வழிப்போக்கன்  🫶🏾🫂
